{"tid":909703,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"依家nba似戰國時代，大部份球隊都有隊中既當家球星","createTime":"2018-11-20T14:53:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-20T20:26:52.000Z","uid":134925,"like":4,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"05b4e26d409b27763bee735e7884d84f9e5ea543","tid":909703,"uid":134925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T14:53:46.000Z","msg":"依家nba大部份球隊都有自已既當家球星，好多隊仲要唔止1個，感覺有d返返以前舊時戰國時代咁，猛將如雲，仲有今年d rookie/ sophomore 好似第1／2季已經打到似模似樣，俾人感覺就係將來球隊既當家球星既材料，好似bos既tatum, kings既fox/buddy, 76ers既embild（ 第3年）/ben simmons, Sun既ayton, 牛仔doncic, jazz既mitchell，nba近呢幾年真係迎來另一次高峰，出產好多猛人，睇返踏入2000年去到00年代尾nba draft，除左03一代整體質數高之外，其他屆水平都一般，得好少簡得落手，連狀元都好水，kwame brown(mj神級眼光) ,bargnani, bogut, oden, <br />\n仲有durant,curry,harden,wb個一批一開始都味打起，當時係不起眼，邊個估到今時今日curry，harden係咁屈機？<br />\n<br />\n各隊既當家球星：<br />\nraptors: Leonard <br />\nbucks: 字母哥，middleton<br />\npacers: oladipo<br />\n76ers: embild,simmons,butler<br />\nbos: irving,tatum,hayward<br />\npistons: griffin,drummond<br />\nmagic: vucevic<br />\nhonets: kemba<br />\nnets: 無<br />\nheat: whiteside<br />\nwizards: wall,beal<br />\nknicks: porzingis<br />\nbulls: lavine<br />\nhawks: 無（young有機會做curry 2世）<br />\ncav: 無<br />\n<br />\nwar: curry,klay<br />\nporlands: lillard, cj<br />\nthunder: wb, pg<br />\nclippers: t.harris<br />\ngrizzles: gasol, conley<br />\nnuggets: yokic<br />\npelicans: ad, holiday<br />\nrockets: harden, cp3<br />\nlakers: king james<br />\njazz: mitchell<br />\nkings: buddy, fox<br />\nspurs: lma, dorozan<br />\ndal: doncic, smith jr<br />\ntimberwolves: kat, wiggins<br />\nsun: booker, ayton"},{"pid":"595c6409d352e0c7ec4a321c8c8d919ef9e0611d","tid":909703,"uid":8636,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T14:56:05.000Z","msg":"唔講遠啲，2000s都係咁<br />\n樓主未出世？"},{"pid":"52015cdb909afccfe88c0429542c1454ebc8fb8f","tid":909703,"uid":95542,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T15:00:16.000Z","msg":"hawks: jeremy lin"},{"pid":"e5b6a0